Beverages

Company Overview of Mirth Provisions, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mirth Provisions, Inc. crafts and produces cannabis-infused edibles and drinkables with local ingredients. The company offers Legal, a concoction soda with cannabis extract; and Drift, a sublingual spray crafted with cold-extracted peppermint oil and cannabis. It sells its products through retail stores in Washington and Oregon. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Longview, Washington.


909 California WayLongview, WA 98632United StatesFounded in 2014



Phone: 360-519-7783

mirthprovisions.com







